<title>USA: Performance Technologies appoints CEO.</title>
<headline>Performance Technologies appoints CEO.</headline>
<dateline>ROCHESTER, N.Y. 1997-06-11</dateline>
<text>
<p>Performance Technologies Inc said on Wednesday that it had appointed president and chief operating officer Donald Turrell to the additional post of chief executive officer.</p>
<p>Turrell succeeds Charles Maginness, who will remain in his his current post of chairman and chief executive officer of the company's San Diego based subsidiary, UconX Corp, the company said in a statement.</p>
